The BalanceManagement interface represents the management of balance in a vending machine, extending the VendingOperations interface.

The CoffeeMachine class represents a Coffee Machine, extending an abstract Vending Machine.

The ExportSnackRunnable class represents a runnable task for exporting snack products from a snack vending machine.

The ImportCoffeeRunnable class represents a runnable task for importing coffee products into a coffee vending machine.

The ImportSnackRunnable class represents a runnable task for importing snack products into a snack vending machine.

Represents an exception thrown when there is insufficient balance in a vending machine.
InsufficientResourceException
Represents an exception thrown when there are insufficient resources to perform an operation in a vending machine.
Main

Represents an exception thrown when a vending machine is out of stock.

The Product class represents a product in the vending machine.

The ProductFactory class provides methods for creating instances of different types of products, including generic products, coffees, and snacks using the abstract factory pattern.
Snack
The Snack class represents a type of product specifically for snacks in the vending machine.
